			&lt;p class=&quot;fontClass auto-style4&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;{!Contact.Name}&lt;/b&gt; from &lt;b&gt;{!Account.Name}&lt;/b&gt; recently completed the annual NCR Customer Relationship Survey and reported an outstanding concern they would like to discuss immediately.&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;p style=&quot;color:red&quot; class=&quot;fontClass auto-style4&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;NOTE:&lt;/b&gt; If you are not the Account Manager for this contact, see instructions below to Change Owner and reassign the case.&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;p class=&quot;fontClass auto-style4&quot;&gt;Please follow-up with this customer as soon as possible to resolve the issue. You can click on the link below to access the case. From there you can click on the customer contact name to view their survey. After following up with the customer, please click on this &lt;a href=&quot;&apos;+Link+&apos;&quot;&gt;Link&lt;/a&gt; and use Edit/Close buttons to update required fields and close the case. Document your action plan in the case and update the status as work progresses to completion.&lt;/p&gt;	
			&lt;h2&gt;&lt;u&gt;HOW TO UPDATE FOLLOW-UP CASE:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
			&lt;ol class=&quot;fontClass auto-style4&quot;&gt;
					&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;CLICK ALERT LINK&lt;/b&gt; in the original alert sent to you, or click link in &lt;b&gt;SUBJECT&lt;/b&gt; column of report to open a specific case.&lt;/li&gt;
					&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;CLICK CHANGE OWNER BUTTON&lt;/b&gt; if necessary to reassign to a different account owner.&lt;/li&gt;
					&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;CLICK CONTACT NAME &lt;/b&gt; to open contact record and view survey feedback with all responses.&lt;/li&gt;
					&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;CLICK BACK &lt;/b&gt;CLICK BACK in your browser to return to the follow-up case so you can edit and make updates.&lt;/li&gt;
					&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;CLICK EDIT BUTTON &lt;/b&gt;in the case to update all required fields including any planned actions.&lt;/li&gt;
					&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;UPDATE STATUS&lt;/b&gt; to reflect your follow-up progress:&lt;/li&gt;
				&lt;dl class=&quot;fontClass auto-style4&quot;&gt;
					&lt;dd&gt;New  – (Default) no action has been taken yet.&lt;/dd&gt;
					&lt;dd&gt;Customer Call Completed – customer discussion documented in case including key issues and planned actions.&lt;/dd&gt;
					&lt;dd&gt;Closed – all actions have been completed by sales and functional teams to address the customer’s concerns.&lt;/dd&gt;
				&lt;/dl&gt;
				&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;CLICK SAVE BUTTON&lt;/b&gt; to save all changes when completed.&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;/ol&gt;
